  @contract  refuse if dest col has any onset in source's row extent (note: note-on; else any event)  @ 2733
  @invariant  source's row extent = selection's [r1,r2] for a block, moved event's onset row for a single  @ 2734
  @invariant  tails (either direction) clipped by tm's tail pass; never block  @ 2735
